&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/important-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Important Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);  &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Present perfect&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;is used to show &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;a finished action with a result in the present&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);  &quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;E.g.&lt;/strong&gt; -&lt;/span&gt;The Mayor has announced a new plan for the railways.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;font-weight: 700; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;The correct sentence&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;- &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-6cd14980-7fff-cf2e-c0ab-79f74ec1544f&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The facial recognition tracking (FRT) system has been rapidly &lt;strong&gt;increased&lt;/strong&gt; in India &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;for surveillance, security or authentication of identity.&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;To make a speech&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The meaning of the idiom&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;To have the floor&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;To have the right to speak at a public meeting&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Example: He stepped aside to allow others&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to have the floor&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;option 4.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;​Fascinate&amp;#39;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The correct spelling is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Fascinate​&amp;#39;,&lt;/strong&gt; which means&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;to interest someone a lot&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;(आकृष्&amp;zwj;ट करना या रुचि जगाना; मोहित करना)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Example:&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;​&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Science has always &lt;strong&gt;fascinated&lt;/strong&gt; me&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;According to the given explanation, &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 3&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the correct answer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;option 2 i.e. B.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There is no error in Parts &amp;#39;A&amp;#39; and &amp;#39;C&amp;#39; of the sentence. It tells about an Indian social reformer.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There is&amp;nbsp;an error&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;part &amp;#39;B&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;of the sentence. The sentence is written in the past perfect tense.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;We use the past perfect simple&lt;strong&gt; (had&amp;nbsp;+ past participle) &lt;/strong&gt;to talk about time up to a certain point in the past.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;​E.g. -&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;We&amp;#39;d finished&lt;/strong&gt; all the water before we were halfway up the mountain.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence is written about an Indian social reformer, who did social work a long time ago. It&amp;nbsp;is not necessary to write down the sentence in the perfect tense.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It should be written in past simple tense. So, &amp;quot;had played&amp;quot; should be replaced by &amp;quot;played&amp;quot;.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The correct sentence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;-&lt;em&gt; &amp;quot;Savitribai Phule, an Indian social reformer, &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;played&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; an important and vital role in improving women&amp;rsquo;s rights in India.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-99eda7e2-7fff-56d7-e451-4f77482e23c5&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;significance&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The passage is about &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Moral values&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;​ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-0f0f1f0a-7fff-2546-d0f7-5b655f336195&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Let us refer to this line from the passage, &amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Moral values hold the same ____(1)____&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; background-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt; across cultures and centuries.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;From the above sentence, we can say that moral values do not change or have the same importance across cultures and centuries and they hold the same &lt;strong&gt;significance&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In &lt;strong&gt;option 2&lt;/strong&gt;, &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;significance&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-c8c7659f-7fff-44aa-f33e-cc900ae493ac&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;means &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;the &lt;strong&gt;quality of being worthy of attention, importance.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-f7f5d527-7fff-3594-925d-fe73033e68bd&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;So, &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;significance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;is the correct word for blank No.1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;​&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-6751c0c2-7fff-65c4-df31-f02ea3327320&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Let us look into the meanings of other words:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;​&lt;strong&gt;responsibility - &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;the state or fact of having a duty to deal with something or of having control over someone.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;
		&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;authority - &lt;/strong&gt;the right or permission to do something&lt;b&gt;.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;
		&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;character - &lt;/b&gt;strong personal qualities​&lt;/div&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;  background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;So the correct sentence is - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Moral values hold the same &lt;strong&gt;significance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt; across cultures and centuries.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;ancient&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

